latestPosts.caption:
masti on my last day in tokyooo 

📍blue bottle coffee, roppongi tokyo

bougie girl’s guide to a perfect day in Tokyo:
	•	stay at Sequence Miyashita Park in Shibuya
	•	start your morning with cheese toast + a flat white at .com space
	•	then, take a peaceful walk through Meiji Jingu Shrine
	•	book an omakase lunch at Sushi Lab, Shibuya
	•	rest up for the afternoon but before that: a milkshake from Kith Treats (non-negotiable)
	•	post nap; recharge with matcha at The Matcha Tokyo
	•	go shopping + window browsing in Omotesando, Aoyama & Cat Street 
	•	end the night with seafood ramen at Oreryu Shin

guaranteed main character energy 🧚🧚🧚

#shibuya #omotensando ##sloreccomends #girlsgirlsgirls #tokyoitinerary #meijijingu #harajuku
